    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One surreal morning, Colin’s apartment door disappears just as he is getting ready for his monotonous job. The apartment turns into a chaotic labyrinth and some inexplicable phenomena shake Colin’s worldview.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/5b7f084dc0c647931acadeeadf465fd5.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/5b7f084dc0c647931acadeeadf465fd5.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/5b7f084dc0c647931acadeeadf465fd5.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cryptic message written on the bathroom mirror, a mysterious puppet in his bedroom, and some emotional challenges terrify Colin. New visitors constantly appear, making Colin question his past, present and future. Will Colin discover a new meaning to his life? Or was it all just a bizarre dream? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Locked in your own apartment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rooms transform, familiar faces appear as creepy characters - and there is no way for you to hide. Face the horror in your own apartment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/164eb523f61e3759e483ff299383ac70.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/164eb523f61e3759e483ff299383ac70.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/164eb523f61e3759e483ff299383ac70.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve multifaceted puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Colin escape from his apartment and decipher hair-raising puzzles, convert household items into useful tools and free yourself from your nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/6d2f43a4ea3a7178a6c5775f906b937e.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/6d2f43a4ea3a7178a6c5775f906b937e.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/6d2f43a4ea3a7178a6c5775f906b937e.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More than 4 hours (in the main game) of exciting and fully soundtracked dialogues</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a professionally dubbed adventure with many interesting characters - brought to life by professional voice actors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/95f57a5389f78b52b8c35de7d6e30e8f.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/95f57a5389f78b52b8c35de7d6e30e8f.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/95f57a5389f78b52b8c35de7d6e30e8f.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lovingly hand drawn and animated</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a hand-drawn masterpiece - full of loving animations and interactions, crazy characters and a constantly changing game world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/688134e1a60ebdb606766e6ac5146b6b.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/688134e1a60ebdb606766e6ac5146b6b.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/688134e1a60ebdb606766e6ac5146b6b.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face Colin‘s fears</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Colin and help him face his fears. Experience a complex adventure full of dry humor between harsh reality an mystical changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/ab1a55cf285c2b584fa747bc1aadcb9b.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/ab1a55cf285c2b584fa747bc1aadcb9b.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/ab1a55cf285c2b584fa747bc1aadcb9b.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Colin’s  thoughs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into Colin’s complex mind and find repressed memories, hidden thought processes, and long-forgotten dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/aa030d4c2b1065db97241c568ea9c00a.poster.avif?t=1728849426\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/aa030d4c2b1065db97241c568ea9c00a.webm?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183630/extras/aa030d4c2b1065db97241c568ea9c00a.mp4?t=1728849426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
